00:50:24.894 --> 00:50:49.894
Incoming livestream: Probably a few. So I've spent a lot of time on this problem. So when you go and try to alert AI investigation of SOC alerts and try to actually get ground truth on which alerts were actually worth investigating and which were false positives, you'll find that there's, like, a double-digit disagreement rate, between SOC analysts, right? So if you're trying to label a SOC alert, like, in the fashion of cat versus dog.


