00:53:24.624 --> 00:53:38.473
Incoming livestream: Okay. So, I don't know how many sort of classical ML people there are in the background, but anybody who studied ML in college or has done a lot of machine learning is familiar with this concept of the oracle, right? So this is the… so I actually brought in a picture, a real-life picture of the oracle here.


