01:02:26.994 --> 01:02:40.144
Incoming livestream: If we can't deploy autonomous systems that can make sensitive changes in our infrastructure with confidence, and knowing they won't break stuff, we're gonna be in serious trouble, and evaluation is, in my mind, the main hard problem there.


